{"remainingRequest":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/index.js??ref--1-1!/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vuepress/lib/webpack/markdownLoader.js??ref--1-2!/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/adaptation/accessibility/understandable/predictable.md?vue&type=template&id=3b986bc2&","dependencies":[{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/adaptation/accessibility/understandable/predictable.md","mtime":1540958169775},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/cache-loader/dist/cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/loaders/templateLoader.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/cache-loader/dist/cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/index.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vuepress/lib/webpack/markdownLoader.js","mtime":1533872387000}],"contextDependencies":[],"result":["\n<div class=\"content\"><h1 id=\"网页以可预见的方式呈现\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#网页以可预见的方式呈现\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 网页以可预见的方式呈现</h1>\n<h2 id=\"描述\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#描述\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 描述</h2>\n<p>让网页内容以可预见的方式呈现，而不发生额外的不符合预期的变化。</p>\n<h2 id=\"例子\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#例子\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 例子</h2>\n<h3 id=\"good-case\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#good-case\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> good case</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>如果页面顶部有一个用来搜索的功能控件其名称为search，那么如果其他位置也有一个相同功能的控件其也应该命名为search，保持一致性以免造成用户的认知混淆</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"指导建议\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#指导建议\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 指导建议</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>确保聚焦事件不导致页面上下文变化</li>\n<li>确保输入事件不导致页面上下文非预期的变化</li>\n<li>确保导航的一致性，在网站中多个网页重复出现的导航，保证一致的相对顺序，除非是用户设置引起的顺序变化</li>\n<li>对于相同功能的呈现尽量使用相同组件，避免引起混淆</li>\n<li>上下文的主要变化只能由用户主动发起，拒绝自动更新</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n",null]}